{"tid":2322404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國駐港總領使館: 非常關注港共叫停BA飛香港航線","createTime":"2020-12-12T09:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T15:03:40.000Z","uid":51271,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9934a1073b89c4055a79be9c7377f0f739885e34","tid":2322404,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T09:55:48.000Z","msg":"UK in Hong Kong<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nWe know that the two-week suspension of British Airways flights incoming from London until 25 December will be worrying for families and people looking to spend Christmas together in #HongKong. We have raised the concerns of those affected with the Hong Kong SAR Government. It is important to tackle the threat of #Covid19 whilst also ensuring that people who need to can continue to travel safely. We hope that any suspension of airlines on these vital routes will be kept to a minimum.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/UKandHongKong/posts/3641039192606149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FUKandHongKong%2Fposts%2F3641039192606149&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcgwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=5cb0286b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/UKandHongKong/posts/3641039192606149</a>"},{"pid":"7e2cef350663936e29af329d3b39a643cd17bced","tid":2322404,"uid":53577,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:00:37.000Z","msg":"幾時武裝國民自衛？"},{"pid":"58c83d89690af72a36fe99221164cd8c4e4685be","tid":2322404,"uid":383914,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:03:18.000Z","msg":"日落國持續關注<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9302ac43604f6107787fc5a34c68cd3ee0c244","tid":2322404,"uid":47356,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T10:03:57.000Z","msg":"為左唔比走&quot;政治犯&quot; 逼英國派母艦黎撤僑, <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/KqahhSR4RAU/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/t